title: Bug 124761: Data not extracted when adding two filters
description: When two filters are added, one being 'State is equal to CA' and the other being 'EmployeeId is Top 10', the data does not get extracted.

SR: To reproduce the issue:1. Import the attached report.2. Preview the report and observe that the data does not get extracted.
